import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):

    v1 = jnp.tanh(x0)
    v2 = jnp.cos(x0)
    v3 = jnp.abs(x1)
    v4 = jnp.cos(v3)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v4, x2)
